# МойСклад API (see PROJECT_CONTEXT)

- **Rate limit:** ~**100 requests per 5 seconds**. In any loop that may issue back-to-back requests, use **`time.sleep(0.1)`** between calls (e.g. between PUTs in batch approve/sync) to stay under the limit.
- **Batch size:** at most **50** products per batch operation (per PROJECT_CONTEXT: batch generate / batch approve).
- **HTTP headers:** **`Authorization: Bearer <token>`** and **`Accept-Encoding: gzip`** (and send requests in a way compatible with compressed responses).
- **Custom attributes in API payload:** read/iterate attributes as a **list** of attribute objects, **not** as a dict keyed by id — code must not assume a map shape.
- **Attribute UUIDs:** do **not** hardcode UUID strings. **Resolve attribute meta by name at app startup** (or first use), then **cache** resolved ids in **`st.session_state`** (or a single app-level cache passed into the client) for the session.
- **Errors:** handle at least:
  - **401** — auth failure: clear message, do not spin retry loops without re-auth
  - **429** — rate limit: back off, optional retry with delay
  - **Other HTTP / network errors** — surface safely, log context, do not leave DB/API in an inconsistent state without documented recovery
- All of the above is implemented **only** in `moysklad_client.py` so the rest of the app calls one module.
Официальная документация МойСклад JSON API 1.2:
https://dev.moysklad.ru/doc/api/remap/1.2/

